\begin_layout Standard
Hello dear reader.
 Thank you for taking a hold of this treatise.
 Let it take you on a journey of discovery through the food chain.
 You're going to learn a lot about the costs of the food we consume.
 This will give you an insight into where, among other things, agriculture
 has an impact.
 For the farmers among you, it can also provide arguments to justify your
 price.
\end_layout

