\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A big exception is the total amount of agricultural land per inhabitant.
 Whereas this currently hovers around 30 ares/inhabits, in the proposed
 scenario it will drop to 12 ares/inhabits, below the minimum limit of 14
 ares/inhabits.
 Won't that put us in dangerous waters?
\end_layout

